```plantuml
@startuml input-output-hk_marlowe-starter-kit

actor Developer
participant "Jupyter Notebook" as JN
participant "Marlowe Runtime" as MR
participant "Wallet (CIP30/CIP45)" as Wallet
participant "Docker Environment" as Docker

Developer -> JN: Start Jupyter Notebook
JN -> Docker: Verify Environment Setup
Docker -> MR: Check Marlowe Runtime Health
JN -> Developer: Environment Verified

Developer -> JN: Run setup/01-setup-keys.ipynb
JN -> Wallet: Create Addresses and Signing Keys
Wallet -> JN: Addresses and Keys Setup
JN -> Developer: Keys Created

Developer -> JN: Run dApp Example
JN -> Wallet: Connect Wallet
Wallet -> JN: Provide Wallet Address
JN -> MR: Create Marlowe Contract
MR -> JN: Contract Created
JN -> Wallet: Sign Transaction
Wallet -> MR: Submit Transaction
MR -> JN: Transaction Submitted

Developer -> JN: Run Command-Line Tool
JN -> MR: Query Contract Status
MR -> JN: Contract Status

Developer -> Docker: Deploy via Docker Compose
Docker -> MR: Start Services (Node, Runtime, etc.)
Docker -> JN: Start Jupyter Notebook
JN -> Developer: Notebook Ready for Interaction

@enduml
```